title: This 'Star Wars'/'Disney' mash-up makes NO sense but we love it
text:
This 'Star Wars'/'Disney' mash-up makes NO sense but we love it USA Today, USAToday.com 7:44 a.m. EDT October 6, 2015 Starwars Disney mashup CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
With Disney on its way to world domination, this mash-up was bound to happen. 
The Star Wars and Disney mash-up trailer edited by PistolShrimps combines two of Disney's greatest properties in the craziest, most magical video that ever existed. Belle as Rey? Gotcha. Rey and Finn running from the Maleficent dragon? Check. There's singing, magic carpet rides, and every other supporting Disney character popping up in the Star Wars: The Force Awakens trailer, and it makes no narrative sense at all, but we love it. 
Now we're going to patiently wait for the mash-up trailer combining Star Wars , Disney and The Avengers for the ultimate #synergy video.
